column5: Heading up to my brothers new place north of Temagami this coming weekend. Any chance finding minnows around NB?  Also any tips on walleye depths ?.  He's on the Montreal river below the dam at Mowats landing. Going to have to dress warm, looks like its going to be chilly.  Thanks!
Call Gramps at Angus Lake (about 10 miles S of Temag) and see what they have in house.  705-569-3825
Lots of places.  Billy Bob's  or Discount tackle would be most convienient for you.  Gramps on hwy 11 by Angus lake is closest to your final destination.  Call in advance to be sure.
